OL,11,
OL,12,CG1998FThe 43rd Eurovision Song Contest
OL,13,Fairs on BBC One, live from Birmingham.
OL,14,FTerry Wogan and Ulrika Jonsson
OL,15,Fpresented, with Wogan also providing
OL,16,Fthe commentary for the UK audience.
OL,17,FImaani came 2nd for the UK and Dana
OL,18,FInternational from Israel won.
